<paragraph blockId="33.[151,1437,1432,1745]" pageId="33" pageNumber="484">
Gills extending from valve VII to valve V, composed of 10 ctenidia on each side in studied specimen (BL 
<quantity metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.0" pageId="33" pageNumber="484" unit="mm" value="5.0">5 mm</quantity>
